{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Good news for those of you who are always &quot;Shotgun Camper&quot;(Corner Camper) in FPS games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This game is a PvE game dedicated to aiming and shooting enemies that emerge from corners.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each round lasts less than 10 seconds. It requires split-second concentration and delicate aiming skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Show off your corner camping and pre-aiming skills to your heart's content.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This game is all about pre-aiming.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">I aimed to capture the thrill you get when you take down an enemy that jumps out at you in a tactical FPS, with micro flicks and lightning-fast reaction times.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Weapons include not just shotgun, but also AR, SMG, and Sniper.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are also Steam rankings (high scores, total kills, etc.), an achievement feature, and an endless mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Stage-based progression lets you enjoy a variety of situations, such as close range, long range, peeking from cover, and simultaneous multi-directional appearances.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It's not only fun as a standalone game but also great for practicing your pre-aiming skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game will not have an Early Access period, but I will be updating the game from time to time with difficulty adjustments, additional content, bug fixes, etc.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Warm-up","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3069490/d126df75df7b0e6ee393258b5c2c8a47dbd58296.jpg"},{"name":"Short-Range","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3069490/c4f6371ad04bfda1a4c8bdd48eb776648d5d4d7e.jpg"},{"name":"Pillars","path":"https://cdn.akamai.s